text: Posts: 54,145 Colts' QB Luck out for second game; Hasselbeck to start (Yahoo Sports) HOUSTON (AP) -- Indianapolis quarterback Andrew Luck was inactive on Thursday night against the Houston Texans because of a right shoulder injury.
